OL,3,CMan is found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cwoman is strangled to death in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,FA man has been found guilty of murder
OL,8,Fafter a woman was attacked and killed
OL,9,Fin Smethwick last year.
OL,11,FShara Millar's body was found by a
OL,12,Fmember of the public just after 6am on
OL,13,F11 August 2025 on Woodburn Road.
OL,15,FShara, 41, was discovered with head
OL,16,Finjuries, and it was clear nothing
OL,17,Fcould be done to save her.
OL,19,FA forensic postmortem examination
OL,20,Fshowed Shara's cause of death was
OL,21,Fstrangulation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
