PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779217874
OL,3,CMan is found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cwoman is strangled to death in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,FJust before 1am, a white sprinter van
OL,8,Fwas shown on CCTV footage pulling into
OL,9,FWoodburn Road.
OL,11,FAt around 1.30am, Shara's body was
OL,12,Fremoved from the back of the van and
OL,13,Fleft on the pavement.
OL,15,FA liquid was also splashed and shaken
OL,16,Fover Shara's body.
OL,18,FEarlier in the night, the van was seen
OL,19,Fon Soho Road, Handsworth and Shara,
OL,20,Faged 41, was seen getting in the van
OL,21,Fon Victoria Road.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
