PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779217874
OL,3,CMan is found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cwoman is strangled to death in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,FOfficers attended the home address of
OL,8,FSingh and was stopped in a vehicle
OL,9,Fnear his house. The 32-year-old was
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,11,Fsubsequently charged.
OL,13,FFollowing a two-week trial, Singh of
OL,14,FLeopard Lane, West Bromwich was
OL,15,Fconvicted of murder and will be
OL,16,Fsentenced on 27 May.
OL,18,FDI Joe Davenport, Homicide Unit, said:
OL,19,F"Shara was brutally killed by a
OL,20,Fdangerous predator.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
