PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779217874
OL,3,CMan is found guilty of murder after
OL,4,Cwoman is strangled to death in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,F"Singh was drinking in a pub earlier
OL,8,Fin the night and visited Soho Road to
OL,9,Flook for sex workers. He then picked
OL,10,FShara up in his van and she was
OL,11,Ffatally attacked.
OL,13,F"He attempted to get rid of any trace
OL,14,Fof his presence by pouring a liquid
OL,15,Fover Shara's body to destroy any
OL,16,Fforensic evidence.
OL,18,F"My thoughts are with Shara's loved
OL,19,Fones, and I thank them for the support
OL,20,Fduring this investigation and trial."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@eO]
